    Page: 435
    Verse: 16
Tags:
  - Smile
---
There are two kinds of smiles, genuine and artificial. Very often we put on
smiles, but the heart does not smile, only the lips and face take part in
it. This is not a real smile. When the heart is filled with joy, it is
reflected on the face as a smile. It is a natural outflow of joy.
